data.revised_prompt: Generate a professional food-photography style image of a 'Honey Bourbon Fizz' cocktail served in a tall, sleek highball glass. The drink should display a gradient of color from a golden amber at the bottom, representing the bourbon and honey syrup layer, to a pale yellow at the top from the fresh lemon juice. Above, 2 oz of translucent club soda adds a bubbly shimmer. A lemon wheel can be seen placed on the rim of the glass, contributing a vibrant yellow to the scene. The ambiance should be gently lit, with natural sunlight from the side casting faint shadows and capturing reflections on the glass and wooden tabletop. The background should be out of focus and muted, highlighting the gorgeous colors and elegant presentation of the cocktail. The image should be high-quality, photorealistic, without any text or watermarks.
